      <div class="mt-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Need Help Understanding Your Coverage?</h2>
        <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">
          Our team can help you navigate insurance requirements and find the best financing options for your bariatric surgery.
        </p>
